aas_core.aas3_0.types.impl

Class EventPayload

  • java.lang.Object
    • aas_core.aas3_0.types.impl.EventPayload
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IClass, IEventPayload

    public class EventPayload
extends Object
implements IEventPayload
    Defines the necessary information of an event instance sent out or received.

    This element is experimental and therefore may be subject to change or may be removed completely in future versions of the meta-model.
